### AMS2025 school Zagreb, day 1, exercise 4:
### Minimize the energy of a LJ system.
###
### 


units lj
atom_style atomic

### read structure from file
read_data struc.lmp

pair_style      lj/cut 2.5
### parameters for LJ: 
### type_i type_j epsilon sigma cutoff
pair_coeff      1 1 1.0 1.0 2.5

mass 1 1.0


### select minimization algorithm:
###   cg = conjugate gradient
min_style cg

thermo_style custom step etotal
thermo 1
dump            1 all custom 1 dump.dat id type x y z fx fy fz


### launch minimization
minimize 1e-4 1e-3 1000 1000
